node.text: Had the best time making chicken tacos with Chef @ruffoibarra ! All donations raised go to @thisisabouthumanity ❤️ So thrilled that for every dollar donated @thelittlemarket is donating $2 to @thisisabouthumanity ! Thank you Ruffo for inviting me to be a part of Taco Tuesday! Next week join Chef Ruffo as he goes live to cook with @michaeltrevino #thisisabouthumanity

node.text: Holy guacamole @nashvilleneat_holly 😱 Thank you @neatmethod for getting the new King Coop unpacked and organized ♥️ Holly, you and your team knocked it out of the park! Thank you for such a warm, and organized 😉, welcome to Nashville! 🐓 For any organization aficionados like myself, head to my stories for some before and afters! #theneatlife

node.text: Used my summer break from social media  to study art of tik toking youth from yesteryears way of staying up on current events…glossy magazines. node.text: Resting Podcasting Face 🎙 Swipe to hear some teasers from a few of our latest episode of @candicekayla The Directionally Challenged Podcast. In the last couple weeks we’ve covered topics like Postpartum care with @thefirstfortydays , @vobonline who received a Guinness World Record becoming the first woman to reach Earth's highest and lowest points, grief and addiction with @wittelstephanie & @jessicacordovakramer , and being a comedian in lockdown during 2020 with @kate.willett 🎙
